\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's actually crazy,\\\" Healy said on stage.\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Healy\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2973}, {\"ngram\": \"stage\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we landed in Dublin Airport this morning, just seeing the reception here - we did not expect this many people to turn out here today, so thank you to everybody for coming along to support us.\\\"\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dublin Airport\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3023}, {\"ngram\": \"the reception\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"this many people\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Becker admitted: \\\"When I heard there was a homecoming I thought it was like when you have your birthday party and you are scared no one's going to show up, that's what I thought, so thank you all so much.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3190, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"score\": 0.9999218984427029, \"rank\": 7.297974901909083e-05, \"text\": \"Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a homecoming\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"your birthday party\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, we got snippets of what it was like at home when we were racing, but nothing compares to actually seeing everybody here 